data.description: Westmeadow Addition home on almost a quarter acre lot walking distance to schools! Pull up to the side facing garage in the large driveway with room for plenty of parking. Warm up by the fireplace while working from home in the living room office area!  Featuring arched windows, new flooring, and french doors, this cozy home is ready for your family! The split floor plan is a must have for privacy, and, the primary ensuite bath offers his and hers closets, stand up shower, and a walk in, jetted tub with lights to really relax after a long day. Walk out the french doors onto a huge deck in the backyard that also offers a sprinkler system and extra large storage building with shelfing for storage. Vivint security system with window sensors, alarm, and camera offer security and the solar panels are great investment that maximizes efficiency with rising electricity prices or outages!
